1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,180 --> 00:00:48,620
=Episode 20=
=Risk It All For You=

11
00:00:49,430 --> 00:00:50,580
I'll check the dressing room.

12
00:01:07,950 --> 00:01:08,790
Mr. Ye Lang,

13
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,510
do you take this woman

14
00:01:10,710 --> 00:01:13,070
to be your wife?

15
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,350
For better or for worse,

16
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,350
for richer or for poorer,

17
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,400
in sickness and in health,

18
00:01:20,070 --> 00:01:21,680
in joy and in sorrow,

19
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:25,280
to love her without reservation,
to remain faithful to her,

20
00:01:25,350 --> 00:01:26,350
forever and always.

21
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,480
Do you?

22
00:01:28,070 --> 00:01:28,910
I do.

23
00:01:29,430 --> 00:01:30,280
I do, too.

24
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,480
Why you?

25
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,240
Where's Jiang Niannian?

26
00:01:50,950 --> 00:01:51,790
Ye Lang.

27
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,040
The priest already read the vows.

28
00:01:54,510 --> 00:01:55,950
We're husband and wife now.

29
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,590
Why are you still obsessed

30
00:01:57,590 --> 00:01:59,280
with a thrice-married woman?

31
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,680
Answer me!

32
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:03,350
Where is Jiang Niannian?

33
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:06,110
You're hurting me, Ye Lang.

34
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,070
Tell me

35
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,680
where she is!

36
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:11,870
She only brings you scandal and trouble.

37
00:02:12,310 --> 00:02:13,190
I'm different.

38
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,630
I'm the one who's right for you.

39
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:18,150
Ye Lang, why can't you see that?

40
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:19,840
I was engaged to Jiang Niannian.

41
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:22,280
You're the one who's delusional.

42
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:25,030
Even if there was an engagement,

43
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:27,080
it should've been between you and me.

44
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,750
Did you forget that auction...

45
00:02:28,870 --> 00:02:29,710
Enough!

46
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:33,630
I told you before

47
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,430
what happened at the auction was a show.

48
00:02:39,150 --> 00:02:41,680
You just never knew your place.

49
00:02:42,870 --> 00:02:43,840
That's not true.

50
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,680
But for Jiang Niannian,

51
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,000
you would've chosen me!

52
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,750
The only person

53
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,680
I've ever loved is Jiang Niannian.

54
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:54,710
Jiang Qingqing,

55
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:57,590
you have no feelings for me either.

56
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,360
You only care about the Li family's wealth.

57
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:02,520
I'll ask you one last time.

58
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,120
Where did you take Jiang Niannian?

59
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,080
Ye Lang.

60
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,080
How could I not have love for you?

61
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:13,080
Doesn't loving your money count?

62
00:03:14,750 --> 00:03:15,960
Since you won't choose me,

63
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:17,400
then go to hell!

64
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:30,920
Li Hong. What are you trying to do?

65
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,030
I swapped the bride at Ye Lang's wedding.

66
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:38,470
Your sweet sister heard about it,

67
00:03:39,750 --> 00:03:41,310
and rushed to put on the gown.

68
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,640
Li Hong.

69
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:44,280
Stop being so stubborn.

70
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:46,430
You're Li family's Second Young Master.

71
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,280
I'm not being stubborn.

72
00:03:49,030 --> 00:03:49,870
Xue.

73
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,520
I'm doing this for us.

74
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,630
You and Ye Lang

75
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,630
are in the way.

76
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,750
Only by getting rid of you both

77
00:03:58,430 --> 00:04:00,280
can Xue and I be truly happy.

78
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,120
Once you do,

79
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,240
there's no turning back.

80
00:04:12,150 --> 00:04:14,240
I killed Liu Yexi myself.

81
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:16,680
It's too late.

82
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,640
Oh, right.

83
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:20,680
And your three ex-husbands.

84
00:04:21,750 --> 00:04:22,590
I killed them too.

85
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,240
Using Liu Yexi's name,

86
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,870
I got them try God No.6.

87
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,430
The side effects made them

88
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,430
die in those "accidents."

89
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:33,390
So it was you.

90
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,360
I had no choice.

91
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:38,070
They had my whole business locked down.

92
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:40,830
And they wanted a bigger cut.

93
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:42,800
It was a total mess.

94
00:04:43,780 --> 00:04:44,820
If I didn't eliminate them,

95
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,430
how could I build my own power?

96
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,070
Anyway, Liu Yexi is already dead.

97
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,750
With a flick of my finger,

98
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,630
I can make her take the blame.

99
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:59,430
She lived all those years,

100
00:04:59,950 --> 00:05:01,190
and this is the only thing

101
00:05:01,980 --> 00:05:03,190
she could do for me, isn't it?

102
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,440
Xue,

103
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:08,830
why don't you praise me?

104
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,000
You've lost your mind.

105
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,520
Xue,

106
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:14,790
don't worry.

107
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:17,680
I'll win everything for you.

108
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,310
Did you record

109
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,270
everything I just said?

110
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,960
Jiang Niannian,

111
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:51,560
I really like your spirit.

112
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,070
Since I like you that much,

113
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,800
let me tell you one more secret.

114
00:06:12,830 --> 00:06:13,670
Take a look.

115
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,190
What is this?

116
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:29,160
Before the anesthesia kicked in,

117
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,430
your brother begged me.

118
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,560
He said,

119
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,840
"I'm begging you."

120
00:06:35,870 --> 00:06:37,000
"Please don't kill me."

121
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,720
"Don't kill me."

122
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:43,040
"Don't kill me. My sister will find you."

123
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,430
Then what?

124
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,040
Jiang Niannian.

125
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,240
I've already got my new heart.

126
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:57,720
I'll never suffer from heart disease.

127
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:00,600
I can do anything I want now.

128
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,150
Oh,

129
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:06,720
Manlong's organ-trafficking dark web

130
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,510
was built by me.

131
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:11,270
At first, I just needed a new heart.

132
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,920
Never thought it'd make me this rich.

133
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:17,000
Li Hong, let her go!

134
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:22,590
Shut up!

135
00:07:22,830 --> 00:07:23,670
Why laughing?

136
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,760
Second Young Master.

137
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,950
How's your

138
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:31,920
phone signal?

139
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:48,540
(Cruel Rich Heir Runs Dark Web Deals)

140
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,360
You're livestreaming?

141
00:08:00,510 --> 00:08:02,390
You planned all this from the start.

142
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:04,230
No.

143
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,520
How did you know?

144
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:07,590
Looks like

145
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,360
you really don't know Ye Lang.

146
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:12,270
Ye Lang found out everything already.

147
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:15,160
So he set this trap just for you.

148
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:26,430
Seeing how miserable you are,

149
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,830
I'll kindly tell you one more truth.

150
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,480
You're not Liu Yexi

151
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,270
and Zhong Minghui's son.

152
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,390
You're actually the Li family's

153
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:39,360
biological son.

154
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:47,800
That's impossible.

155
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,550
You're lying to me!

156
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,910
How pitiful Liu Yexi is.

157
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:55,550
She spent her whole life paving your way.

158
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:58,200
And you sent her straight to ruin.

159
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,630
What a joke.

160
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,630
Liu Yexi

161
00:09:03,150 --> 00:09:04,630
is just trash.

162
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:08,000
In this world,

163
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:09,870
the one who loves me most is Xue.

164
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,920
Xue,

165
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,270
you won't leave me, right?

166
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,920
Say it.

167
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,270
You love me, right?

168
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,720
I'm useless.

169
00:09:29,510 --> 00:09:30,480
My fault.

170
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:35,390
I kept letting you down.

171
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:38,200
I'll kill Jiang Niannian right now.

172
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:55,200
Don't!

173
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,200
I know what you just said

174
00:09:58,030 --> 00:09:59,550
was to stall for time.

175
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:03,360
You're expecting Ye Lang to save you?

176
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:05,230
Listen,

177
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,150
Ye Lang is already dead.

178
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,320
Ye Lang...

179
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:14,920
Why are you here?

180
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,680
What?

181
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:22,870
You're disappointed

182
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,320
I'm not dead?

183
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:50,840
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

184
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:58,880
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

185
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:06,440
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

186
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,640
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

187
00:11:09,640 --> 00:11:14,640
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

188
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:18,880
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

189
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:23,320
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

190
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:27,160
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

191
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:32,920
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

192
00:11:32,920 --> 00:11:37,240
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

193
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:41,080
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

194
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:45,600
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

195
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:50,440
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

196
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:57,400
♪Life finds its way again♪
